@compile instruction
javac *.java

@Server excution instruction
sudo java Server [-u] <portnumber>
-u : using UDP protocol instead of TCP

@Client excution instruction
java Client [-u] <hostname> <portnumber>
-u : using UDP protocol instead of TCP

@Client valid command
put <key> <value>
get <key>
del <key>

@log files
each type of servers and clients has its own .log file, ig. TCPServer.log, UDPServer.log, TCPClient.log and UDPClient.log.

@Script test
java Client [-u] <hostname> <portnumber> < <scriptfile>
scriptfile: there are two scripts, which are test.in command_script.txt

